[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":204},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20191003\u002F3790268908\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20191003\u002F3790268908\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20191003\u002F3790268908\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20191003\u002F3790268908\u002F":179,"related:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20191003\u002F3790268908\u002F":188},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2019\u002F10\u002F03\u002Fjs-from-zero-18-localstorage\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":162,"date":163,"description":18,"extension":164,"lang":165,"meta":166,"navigation":167,"path":168,"readingMinutes":169,"seo":170,"standalone":171,"stem":172,"tags":173,"tldr":176,"updated":176,"url":177,"__hash__":178},"content\u002FRE：從零開始的學習 JS 生活\u002FEP-18-RE：從零開始的學習-JS-生活-第十八日.md","EP.18 RE：從零開始的學習 JS 生活-第十八日之 localStorage","3790268908",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":149},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,29,32,36,44,51,54,60,64,75,80,84,94,99,103,110,115,118,121,125,128,135,138,143,146],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"轉生第十八日，這一篇將會介紹另一種儲存方式，也就是 localStorage。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"localstorage","localStorage",[16,24,25],{},"localStorage 是 HTML5 才加入的新技術，主要可以分為兩種，一種是 sessionStorage，以及這一篇要介紹的 localStorage，那這兩種最主要的差異只在於生命週期的不同。",[16,27,28],{},"一般來講我們網頁若要暫時儲存某些資料時，可以選擇儲存在 Cookie 中，但是 Cookie 可以儲存的大小只有 4 KB，只要稍微大一點就爆了，所以 Cookie 通常會比較常見於儲存登入資訊，那若如果要儲存的資料大於 4 KB 就可以改用 localStorage。",[16,30,31],{},"另外 localStorage 的資料是可以永久保存的，除非使用者去刪除它，否則 localStorage 的資料將會一直存在瀏覽器中。",[12,33,35],{"id":34},"設置-localstorage","設置 localStorage",[16,37,38,39,43],{},"設置 localStorage 之前必須知道一件事情，localStorage 只接受字串格式，所以如果是存入物件類型的資料，就必須搭配 ",[40,41,42],"code",{},"JSON.stringify()"," 的語法一起使用，如果只是單純存入字串，那就只需要這樣寫即可 ↓",[16,45,46],{},[47,48],"img",{"alt":49,"src":50},"localStorage 設置","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FmZ8OQlR.png",[16,52,53],{},"設置成功後就可以在 application → Local Storage 中找到剛剛設置的資料 ↓",[16,55,56],{},[47,57],{"alt":58,"src":59},"Image","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FII36KBu.png",[12,61,63],{"id":62},"讀取-localstorage","讀取 localStorage",[16,65,66,67,70,71,74],{},"讀取的方式非常簡單，只需要將 ",[40,68,69],{},"setItem"," 換成 ",[40,72,73],{},"getItem"," 並帶入名稱就可以了 ↓",[16,76,77],{},[47,78],{"alt":63,"src":79},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FaFvAU5c.png",[12,81,83],{"id":82},"刪除指定-localstorage","刪除指定 localStorage",[16,85,86,87,90,91,93],{},"刪除指定的方式是使用 ",[40,88,89],{},"removeItem"," 的方式也與 ",[40,92,73],{}," 類似 ↓",[16,95,96],{},[47,97],{"alt":83,"src":98},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FdtzS1Ms.png",[12,100,102],{"id":101},"清除全部-localstorage","清除全部 localStorage",[16,104,105,106,109],{},"清除全部 localStorage 則是使用 ",[40,107,108],{},"clear()","，這樣子就會清除 localStorage 底下所有資料 ↓",[16,111,112],{},[47,113],{"alt":102,"src":114},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F6m6OHcG.png",[12,116,117],{"id":117},"那更新呢",[16,119,120],{},"更新的 localStorage 就是設置 localStorage 的方式，只需要重新覆蓋就可以更新了。",[12,122,124],{"id":123},"localstorage-實際應用","localStorage 實際應用",[16,126,127],{},"在這邊有一個範例可以參考，是我之前做的 AQI 空氣品質的小練習",[16,129,130],{},[131,132,134],"a",{"href":133},"\u002FvuejsAQI\u002F","AQI 空氣品質",[16,136,137],{},"都點擊星號時，就會把關注的程式加入至 localStorage 中，進而下次可以快速查看 ↓",[16,139,140],{},[47,141],{"alt":134,"src":142},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FNJXVHB8.png",[12,144,145],{"id":145},"結尾",[16,147,148],{},"下一篇的 RE：從零開始的學習 JS 生活-第十九日 將會介紹 this。",{"title":150,"searchDepth":151,"depth":151,"links":152},"",2,[153,154,155,156,157,158,159,160,161],{"id":14,"depth":151,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":151,"text":22},{"id":34,"depth":151,"text":35},{"id":62,"depth":151,"text":63},{"id":82,"depth":151,"text":83},{"id":101,"depth":151,"text":102},{"id":117,"depth":151,"text":117},{"id":123,"depth":151,"text":124},{"id":145,"depth":151,"text":145},"JavaScript","2019-10-03 00:00:01","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fre-js\u002Fep-18-re-js","1",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"RE：從零開始的學習 JS 生活\u002FEP-18-RE：從零開始的學習-JS-生活-第十八日",[162,174,175],"RE：從零開始的學習 JS 生活","第 11 屆 iT邦幫忙鐵人賽",null,"\u002Fjavas